          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Samples were prepared using RbCl of natural isotopic",
                "abundance(95%). The powder was sedimented on an",
                "aluminium backing (15 mm in dia, 0.1 mm thick) and",
                "covered with a 0.01-mm-thick Al foil. This way samples",
                "were obtained with contents of 0.010-0.030 g/cm**2. The",
                "sample thickness was determined by weighing.",
                "Production yields of Sr-82 and Sr-85 were measured",
                "experimentally using thick RbCl-nat targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
